Package io.opencaesar.oml

Interface RelationInstanceReference

All Superinterfaces:
DescriptionStatement, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NamedInstanceReference, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Reference, Statement
All Known Implementing Classes:
RelationInstanceReferenceImpl
public interface RelationInstanceReference extends NamedInstanceReference
A representation of the model object 'Relation Instance Reference'. RelationInstanceReference is a reference to a relation instance that can be used to add other types to it.

The following features are supported:

  • Instance
  • Owned Types
